title: Raised Fist - All six studio albums (1998-2015) [FLAC]
description:
All six full studio albums released to date by Raised Fist. 1998 - 2015.

All in lossless FLAC, ripped from CD using EAC except Dedication and Veil of Ignorance, that were downloaded (in FLAC) and controlled with spectrogram.


1998 - Fuel
2000 - Ignoring the Guidelines
2002 - Dedication
2006 - Sound of the Republic
2009 - Veil of Ignorance
2015 - From the North
